# Playwright e2e tests run with a local Next.js dev server and mocked
# backend (see playwright.config.ts / tests/mock-server/). No real
# credentials are required — auth is faked via a session cookie minted
# from NEXTAUTH_SECRET. Leave this file empty unless you need to override
# the defaults below.

# NEXTAUTH_SECRET=test-secret-do-not-use-in-prod
